title: R Kelly - Trapped In The Closet (Chapters 1 - 22).mp4
description:
I've come up with a lot of awful Trapped in the Closet uploads:

* The Youtube Playlist is censored, and a few of the episodes have the ending cut off.

* A bunch of the videos are in XviD format like it's still 2005

* A bunch of the videos are censored and with awful audio quality

So here's to being different! These are the first 2 parts of the series, a wild ride of plot twists and bizarre circumstances
